<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>En Popüler Gezilecek Yerler</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-xOolHFLEh07PJGoPkLv1IbcEPTNtaed2xpHsD9ESMhqIYd0nLMwNLD69Npy4HI+N" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.1/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        h1, h2 {
            color: #000000;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .baslik.mt-4 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .image-container:hover {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>
    {{>header}}
    <div class="container">
        <section class="baslik mt-4 text-center">
            <h1 style="margin-top: 20px;">En Popüler Gezilecek Yerler</h1>
            <p style="text-align: justify; margin: 20px 40px;">
                Paris'in romantizmi, Roma'nın tarihi dokusu, Maldivler'in berrak suları... Dünyanın en popüler destinasyonları, 
                sizi unutulmaz deneyimlerle buluşturuyor. Hayalinizdeki tatil için harika bir başlangıç yapmaya hazır mısınız?
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="baslik mt-4 ">
            <img src="images/londra.webp" alt="Keşfet" class="img-fluid my-4 " style="width: 100%;">
            <div class="londra-listesi ">
                <di>
                <h2 class="text-left" style="margin-left: 40px;">Londra</h2>
                <ol class="text-left" style="color: #666; display: inline-block; vertical-align: ">
                    <li>Tower of London</li>
                    <li>Shakespeare's Globe Theatre</li>
                    <li>St. Paul's Cathedral</li>
                    <li>Borough Market</li>
                    <li>Highgate Cemetery</li>
                </ol>
                </di>

               <div class="d-flex" >
                    <h5 class="point">4.5</h5>
                    <div class="ratings" style="margin-left: 20px;">
                        <i class="fa fa-star rating-color"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-star rating-color"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-star rating-color"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-star rating-color"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="review-count">12 Reviews</h5>
                </div>
            </div>

        </section>
    </div>

    {{>footer}} 

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
